{"tid":474361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[禮義之邦] 鹹濕婚鬧無極限 新娘慘遭男賓輪流猥褻","createTime":"2017-11-20T05:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T16:05:01.000Z","uid":121711,"like":15,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0673074909cd68b752db0f8a7e36e40c6498e9a4","tid":474361,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Zivxz_imHpyQAIzc5DRjaA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/7557a387548128d09e0a16e7ad1d1880\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZivxz_imHpyQAIzc5DRjaA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F7557a387548128d09e0a16e7ad1d1880&h=80fa2cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國大陸許多地區都有鬧洞房的習俗，但近幾年卻越玩越過頭，讓原本開開心心的婚禮，瞬間變成新娘的夢魘。近日在微博上瘋傳一段鬧洞房的影片，一名新郎遭一票男賓客架開，新娘則遭其他男賓客硬壓上床猥褻，一旁圍觀的親友不僅沒有上前制止還哈哈大笑，簡直把低俗當有趣。<br />\n<br />\n影片中，新郎和新娘入洞房以後，幾名男賓客先是壓制住坐在新娘旁邊的新郎，接著其中一名男賓竟當著新郎的面，直接將新娘撲倒在床大肆摸胸，輪到另一名男賓客時更變本加厲，不僅將全身緊貼在新娘身上，還一路從嘴唇吻到胸口，完全不把一旁的新郎放在眼裡。過程中，遭受男賓客輪番猥褻的新娘一度掙脫想要離開，卻又再度被拉回來，而一旁圍觀的親友不但沒有人制止，甚至一邊大笑一邊觀看這齣「好戲」。<br />\n<br />\n類似變態婚鬧不只一樁，過去曾發生有新娘慘遭男賓多P輪姦，也有伴娘遭揉胸、摸下體的案例。此外，中國大陸的婚鬧不止「玩色」還「玩命」，日前有親友一時太興奮，在婚禮上拿著滅火器朝新郎狂噴，怎料新郎疑吸入過多乾粉當場昏迷，差點從喜事變喪事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%B9%B9%E6%BF%95%E5%A9%9A%E9%AC%A7%E7%84%A1%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90%E3%80%80%E6%96%B0%E5%A8%98%E6%85%98%E9%81%AD%E7%94%B7%E8%B3%93%E8%BC%AA%E6%B5%81%E7%8C%A5%E8%A4%BB-022945121.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25B9%25B9%25E6%25BF%2595%25E5%25A9%259A%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%2599%2590%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A8%2598%25E6%2585%2598%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25B3%2593%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E6%25B5%2581%25E7%258C%25A5%25E8%25A4%25BB-022945121.html&d=s5%2BDHZkeGHiw0ctAYStYK7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d8304ff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%B9%B9%E6%BF%95%E5%A9%9A%E9%AC%A7%E7%84%A1%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90%E3%80%80%E6%96%B0%E5%A8%98%E6%85%98%E9%81%AD%E7%94%B7%E8%B3%93%E8%BC%AA%E6%B5%81%E7%8C%A5%E8%A4%BB-022945121.html</a><br />\n<br />\n為何男賓客不是我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb926031a78e8e5885dedf4d39b9cd3960103e15","tid":474361,"uid":17081,"like":39,"dislike":4,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.plurk.com/6esCDUDWYwSdkpKalXiabg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.plurk.com%2F6esCDUDWYwSdkpKalXiabg.jpg&h=101a0c20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"072a316d7ce835d8ce821e24af40116b42c69d0f","tid":474361,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2267ef9be435d9171963cdac369ff14c03c69b9f","tid":474361,"uid":65530,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce29c64b08f8dc3bf8c10f6f1a276066f88ab079","tid":474361,"uid":79563,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:10:54.000Z","msg":"嗰班嫁支那蝗既港女唔知有無被多P輪姦？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22d146ed7f71d353069e7ee31a6b3967c24810a","tid":474361,"uid":121711,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"其實點解d男賓客唔直接屌埋個新娘? 直頭黎個多p洞房啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85be62797b81018436540334892b8c79ab8197a6","tid